Question: How would you invite your friends to a party if phones and the Internet did not exist?
Answer:
if phones and the internet did not exist, i will ask my friend to a party in person.if i cannot meet him or her, i will ask a friend of mine who may meet that person, though this would be a little bit inconvenient. if these do not work, i will write a letter a week or two weeks ago, making sure he or she will receive it.